## Why this project

The old portfolio made publishing difficult because every change required touching page markup directly.

## What changed

- Added typed content collections for projects, tech posts, and movie reviews.
- Added dynamic detail routes driven by frontmatter and MDX body content.
- Kept the site static so deployment stays simple and fast.

## Outcome

Publishing now means creating a single MDX file with frontmatter and content.
